#### Docker Container



#### act

For testing the GitHub Actions workflow locally before pushing it.

1. Install act and check if it worked

    ```
    curl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nektos/act/master/install.sh | sudo bash
    ```
    ```
    act --version
    ```

2. Run act

    ```
    act -v
    ```

    When it asks you to choose a default image, choose Medium or Large (since Small is too small for gcc and python).